This restaurant serves Chicago style Italian food.
I have been a regular customer since 2005, great Pizzas you can customize with your choice of toppings.
Food is good and yes their Kitchen is very clean, the bar is a fun place to be.
Bar is open 24/7 and if ou sit there long enough you will meet caste of characters all funnier than hell.
